    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait bell's palsy? i thought that was just for the face. his arm is what feels numb though. and you're saying he needs steroids and an IV? that sounds really intense for just being tired from a flight. are you sure it's not just dehydration or something from the jet lag? he doesn't really want to go to the hospital if it's not an emergency.",
