      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait, you're saying steroids can help a stroke if you start them quickly? i thought you only go to the hospital for those. if he's gonna stay home and try the B12 and the steroids like you said, how much of the methylprednisolone should he actually take? you said 1 gram, is that like one pill or do we need to find a way to do an IV at home? i'm really nervous about the hospital visit so i just want to be sure we're doing the right thing here.",
